1. # Introduction {#introduction}

Private messaging allows companies, volunteers and System Administrators to communicate with each other. 

* Volunteers  
  * Volunteers  
  * Pro Volunteers  
  * Applicants  
    * Volunteers who have applied for an Opportunity  
    * Pro Volunteers who have applied for an Opportunity  
* Companies  
  * Not yet subscribed to a plan \- can only message and respond to System Administrators.  
  * Plan 1 \- Standard Plan  
  * Plan 2 \- Essential Plan  
  * Plan 3 \- Advanced plan  
  * Churn \- subscription cancelled  
* Employees of Customers  
  * Employees of Customers can message Volunteers.  
* Volunteers of Customers  
  * Only after Volunteers have been added to a Customer’s team can they message other Volunteers.  
* System Administrators  
  * System Admin  
  * Support Team Members  
  * etc

Question: Is it the company that messages Volunteers or the team members of companies, which include employees and volunteers?

2. # Settings {#settings}

Settings shall be configurable from the System Admin Dashboard. The System Admin should be able to message anyone. 

## 2.1 Company profiles {#2.1-company-profiles}

Company Profile Display messaging settings (who can message Companies):

|  | Volunteers | PRO Volunteers | Volunteer Applicants | Companies | Customers |
| :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- |
| Setting 1 | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Setting 2 | Yes | Yes | Yes |  | Yes |
| Setting 3 | Yes | Yes | Yes |  |  |
| Setting 4 (default setting) |  | Yes | Yes |  |  |
| Setting 5 |  |  | Yes |  |  |
| Setting 6 |  | Yes |  |  |  |

## 2.2 Volunteer Profiles {#2.2-volunteer-profiles}

Volunteer Profile Display messaging settings (who can message Volunteers):

|  | Volunteers | PRO Volunteers | Companies | Plan 1 Customers | Plan 2 Customers |
| :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- | :---- |
| Setting 1 | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Setting 2 |  | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |

3. # Contact buttons {#contact-buttons}

## 3.1 Company Profile Display {#3.1-company-profile-display}

The Company Profile Display shall have a “Message” button. See example [https://v2.skilledup.life/company/ebdex21](https://v2.skilledup.life/company/ebdex21) 

## 3.2 Volunteer Profile Display {#3.2-volunteer-profile-display}

The Volunteer Profile Display shall have a “Message” button. See example   
[https://v2.skilledup.life/company/ebdex12](https://v2.skilledup.life/company/ebdex12) 

4. # Messaging  {#messaging}

Visit Figma for the latest [designs](https://www.figma.com/design/e7ThrTPKd3gv5bsP1x0Eiq?node-id=1403-12217#1033609311).
